cslver.h File Reference

Chip Support Library (CSL) Version Definitions. More...

Macros

#define CSL_VERSION_ID   (0x03030011U)
 This is the CSL Version. Versions numbers are encoded in the following format: 0xAABBCCDD -> Arch (AA); API Changes (BB); Major (CC); Minor (DD)
 
#define CSL_VERSION_STR   "CSL Revision: 03.03.00.17"
 This is the version string which describes the CSL along with the date and build information.
